Package: progressr
Version: 0.0.0-9001
Title: A Unifying API for Progress Updates
Description: A minimal API for reporting progress updates upstream.  The design is to separate the representation of progress updates from how they are presented.  What type of progress to signal is controlled by the developer.  How this progress updates are rendered is controlled by the end user.
